WEBVTT

00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:04.480
Hola chicos! Come with me on my presentation day!

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:24.600
It's been brilliant so far it's a dream come true, best day of my life.

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:27.400
I'm here to win trophies, I'm here to continue writing the history

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:28.840
of the club. Hopefully we'll do it.

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:50.800
Good afternoon and welcome to Real Madrid City,

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:57.600
Today is a day of great emotion and excitement for all madridistas.

00:00:58.080 --> 00:01:00.320
It's one of those days when we should feel very proud

00:01:00.360 --> 00:01:04.000
because one of the best players in the world has come to Real Madrid.

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:17.680
Hello everyone. Hola Madridistas. I just want to say thank you

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:21.040
everyone in the room and everyone watching online for joining me

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:25.800
for the proudest day of my life the day where I joined the greatest

00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:27.640
football club in the history of the game.

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:31.200
So thank you very much and finally, Hala Madrid!

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:48.560
It's beautiful isn't it?

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.480
The front's better but the back's not bad as well.

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:52.400
The number?

00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:58.040
Yeah, it's amazing. To carry on the legacy of one of my favorite players.

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:36.360
See you soon!
